properties.sfomuseum:description: Stock certificate issued to John A. Hambleton for 5 shares of Aviation Corporation of the Americas; certificate number O 346, dated November 8, 1928; orange and white; official corporate seal impression and original signatures of E. S. (Sally) Swaggerty, Assistant Secretary, and C. V. Whitney, President; signed on reverse by Hambleton April 18, 1929; countersigned November 8, 1928 by The Equitable Trust Company of New York, registered November 9, 1928 by The New York Trust Company; certificate note by American Bank Note Company; document defaced by hole punch cancellation at lower right.
